OL,3,CHull owner calls for play-off final to
OL,4,Cgo ahead amid spygate row
OL,6,FHull City's owner Acun Ilicali says
OL,7,Ftheir Championship play-off final must
OL,8,Fgo ahead despite the ongoing "spygate"
OL,9,Frow involving rivals Southampton and
OL,10,FMiddlesbrough.
OL,12,FThe Tigers are due to face Southampton
OL,13,Fat Wembley on Saturday with promotion
OL,14,Fto the Premier League on the line.
OL,16,FBut Saints, who beat Boro in extra
OL,17,Ftime in the second leg of their semi-
OL,18,Ffinal, are embroiled in a dispute over
OL,19,Fclaims they carried out a spying
OL,20,Fmission at Middlesbrough's Rockliffe
OL,21,FPark training ground.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779289870
OL,3,CHull owner calls for play-off final to
OL,4,Cgo ahead amid spygate row
OL,6,FThe EFL is due to decide whether
OL,7,FSouthampton will face any sanction,
OL,8,Fincluding possible elimination, by
OL,9,FTuesday.
OL,11,FMiddlesborough have called for Saints
OL,12,Fto be kicked out of the final.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV Calendar, Mr Ilicali
OL,15,Fcalled on the EFL not to "spoil our
OL,16,Fbeautiful fans' beautiful day".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779289870
OL,3,CHull owner calls for play-off final to
OL,4,Cgo ahead amid spygate row
OL,6,FHe added: "This game has to be played
OL,7,Fon Saturday because even the damage
OL,8,F(to) our fans, organisations, the
OL,9,Fdamage (to) the club, or psychological
OL,10,Fdamage - everything will be a very big
OL,11,Fmess.
OL,13,F"So, our expectation and my
OL,14,Fexpectation is you play the game, you
OL,15,Fgive whatever decision you can give
OL,16,Fbefore the game (or) after the game,
OL,17,Fbut let the game play."
OL,19,F'We have a beautiful team'
OL,26,@pD@ApmpD@DpnqD@HpmqD@KpnxD@QpmxD@Tpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
