PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779289870
OL,3,CHull owner calls for play-off final to
OL,4,Cgo ahead amid spygate row
OL,6,FThe spygate controversy broke out
OL,7,Ffollowing allegations from
OL,8,FMiddlesbrough that a member of
OL,9,FSouthampton staff - since named as an
OL,10,Fanalyst intern - secretly filmed a
OL,11,Ftraining session two days before their
OL,12,Fsemi-final.
OL,14,FThe man is said to have refused to
OL,15,Fidentify himself to Middlesbrough
OL,16,Fstaff and deleted some content off his
OL,17,Fphone before running into the golf
OL,18,Fclub toilets, changing his clothes and
OL,19,Fleaving the site.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779289870
OL,3,CHull owner calls for play-off final to
OL,4,Cgo ahead amid spygate row
OL,6,FAn independent disciplinary commission
OL,7,Fwill decide if Saints have broken rule
OL,8,F127 - the clause introduced after
OL,9,FLeeds spied on Derby's training ground
OL,10,Fin 2019.
OL,12,FWith promotion to the Premier League
OL,13,Fsaid to be worth about #170 million,
OL,14,Fthe play-off final is known as the
OL,15,Frichest game in football and the
OL,16,Fconsequences of missing out are
OL,17,Fpotentially huge.
OL,19,FBut there is no precedent for the
OL,20,Fcurrent situation.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779289870
OL,3,CHull owner calls for play-off final to
OL,4,Cgo ahead amid spygate row
OL,6,FMr Ilicali said the controversy had
OL,7,F"overshadowed" Hull's achievement in
OL,8,Fbeating Millwall to make the final.
OL,10,F"But it's not like end of the world
OL,11,Ffor us," he added. "I wouldn't say
OL,12,Fthat we are unhappy, but as at the end
OL,13,Fof the day, we have a beautiful team
OL,14,Fthat made us proud all season.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779289870
OL,3,CHull owner calls for play-off final to
OL,4,Cgo ahead amid spygate row
OL,6,F"And our fans are in love with our
OL,7,Fplayers and coach, so we are
OL,8,Fcompletely united. So, I can say that
OL,9,Fthe joy of being in the final and one
OL,10,Fof the biggest games in the world,
OL,11,Fbeing a team there and representing
OL,12,Fthis beautiful city and fans, I think,
OL,13,Fis a big honour."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
